ote>最近foodpanda 加料依個話題炒到好熱<br />\n有張新圖係係tg group搵出黎<br />\n今次真係唔係外賣仔玩野<br />\n係foodpanda 引以為傲既系統同埋佢班cs夾手夾腳將車手單硬塞比步兵做<br />\n再要個客等得耐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8YfKBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8YfKBM.jpg&h=a65f9bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QS9Oj98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQS9Oj98.jpg&h=85b58ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3i3Tu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3i3Tu8.jpg&h=42a1b7db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pyLnou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pyLnou.jpg&h=0dca378a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有圖有真相<br />\nFoodpanda 成日講外賣25分鐘送到<br />\n但原來三公里都照比步兵做<br />\n仲要係客易變壞既甜品<br />\n大家睇完之後如果仲想叫係可以既<br />\n但教教大家記得同foodpanda 反映番d野食遲到係會凍哂<br />\n凍哂點食？一係重做一係退錢啦或者就重做完又退錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好縱容foodpanda 用d咁既理由欺壓步兵<br />\n你唔叫佢回水佢又繼續過左海又神仙喇</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2425a04e91bb71a2338e77243613bc2b24207716","tid":2021174,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6PR2to.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6PR2to.png&h=664c103c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDcgt8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDcgt8p.jpg&h=8ff47eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVrQyz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVrQyz5.jpg&h=8cc45e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8yfKGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8yfKGM.png&h=5dacfa96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0WMRmN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0WMRmN.png&h=dfe26206&s={SIZE}\